csci331.team.red.client

Class ClientEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.Game
      • csci331.team.red.client.ClientEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.badlogic.gdx.ApplicationListener

    public class ClientEngine
extends com.badlogic.gdx.Game
    CSCI331T LD Interface The ClientEngine is the main interface for the clientside / graphics portion of the game to interface with the server. It exposes the public methods necessary for the server to control the game client via the network.
